<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sigillum Maximum — The Seal of the Seven Secrets</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Sigillum Maximum is an epic fantasy series by Eleanor Lian. A princess. Seven seals. One choice that will save — or shatter — the Great Universal Realm.">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Sigillum Maximum — The Seal of the Seven Secrets">
    <meta property="og:description" content="An epic fantasy series by Eleanor Lian. A princess. Seven seals. One choice that will save — or shatter — the Great Universal Realm.">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/images/1. AILEEN NELLA SUA CASETTA SULL'ALBERO.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'%3E%3Ctext y='.9em' font-size='90'%3E🗝️%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            background: #0a0a0f;
            color: #e0dcd5;
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-weight: 700; color: #f0e8d8; }
        a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
        img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
        .section { padding: 100px 0; }
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #a09888;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .gold { color: #d4a747; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #d4a747;
            color: #0a0a0f;
            border: 2px solid #d4a747;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #e8c86a;
            border-color: #e8c86a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(212, 167, 71, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: #d4a747;
            border: 2px solid rgba(212, 167, 71, 0.4);
        }
        .btn-outline:hover { border-color: #d4a747; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        /* === NAV === */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
            padding: 16px 0; transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: transparent;
        }
        .navbar.scrolled {
            background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 167, 71, 0.15);
        }
        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .nav-logo { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #d4a747; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
        .nav-logo span { color: #f0e8d8; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
        .nav-links a {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #a09888;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: #d4a747; }
        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0;
            width: 0; height: 1px; background: #d4a747;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }
        .nav-toggle { display: none; background: none; border: none; color: #f0e8d8; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; }

        /* === HERO === */
        .hero {
            position: relative; min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: url('images/2. Dorcha, cavaliere nero.png') center center / cover no-repeat;
            filter: brightness(0.35) saturate(0.8);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            transition: transform 8s ease;
        }
        .hero:hover .hero-bg { transform: scale(1.1); }
        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10,10,15,0.3) 0%, rgba(10,10,15,0.6) 40%, rgba(10,10,15,0.9) 80%, #0a0a0f 100%);
        }
        .hero-content {
            position: relative; z-index: 2;
            text-align: center; padding: 0 24px; max-width: 900px;
        }
        .hero-tag {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #d4a747; margin-bottom: 24px;
            opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s 0.3s forwards;
        }
        .hero-tag::before, .hero-tag::after { content: '— '; color: rgba(212,167,71,0.4); }
        .hero-tag::after { content: ' —'; }
        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-weight: 900;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5.5rem); line-height: 1.1;
            color: #f0e8d8; margin-bottom: 12px;
            opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s 0.5s forwards;
        }
        .hero-title em {
            font-style: normal;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4a747, #e8c86a, #f0e8d8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
            color: #c0b8a8; letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-bottom: 32px;
            opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s 0.7s forwards;
        }
        .hero-logline {
            font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-style: italic;
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
            color: #e0dcd5; line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 48px;
            opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s 0.9s forwards;
        }
        .hero-buttons { opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s 1.1s forwards; }
        .hero-scroll {
            position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #a09888; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite; cursor: pointer; z-index: 2;
        }
        .hero-scroll svg { display: block; margin: 8px auto 0; }
        @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes bounce { 0%,100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); } }

        /* === LOGLINE BANNER === */
        .logline-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212,167,71,0.08) 0%, rgba(10,10,15,1) 50%, rgba(212,167,71,0.08) 100%);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.1);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.1);
            padding: 48px 24px; text-align: center;
        }
        .logline-banner p {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
            color: #e0dcd5; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }
        .logline-banner .highlight { color: #d4a747; }

        /* === STORY === */
        .story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
        .story-image { border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .story-image img { width: 100%; height: 450px; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.6s; }
        .story-image:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .story-text h3 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #d4a747; }
        .story-text p { margin-bottom: 16px; color: #c0b8a8; font-size: 1.05rem; }
        .story-text .quote {
            font-style: italic; color: #d4a747; font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-left: 2px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.3);
            padding-left: 20px; margin: 24px 0;
        }

        /* === CHARACTERS === */
        .characters-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 32px;
        }
        .character-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.1);
            border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.4s; cursor: pointer;
        }
        .character-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: rgba(212,167,71,0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        .character-card img { width: 100%; height: 260px; object-fit: cover; }
        .character-info { padding: 16px 20px 20px; }
        .character-info h4 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .character-info .role {
            font-size: 0.8rem; color: #d4a747;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .character-info .desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #a09888; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5; }

        /* === REALMS === */
        .realms-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }
        .realm-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px 24px; transition: all 0.4s;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .realm-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--r-color, #d4a747), transparent);
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        .realm-card:hover { border-color: rgba(212,167,71,0.2); transform: translateY(-4px); }
        .realm-card h4 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--r-color, #d4a747); }
        .realm-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #a09888; line-height: 1.6; }
        .realm-card .rune { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; opacity: 0.6; }

        /* === AUTHOR === */
        .author-section { text-align: center; }
        .author-card {
            max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px; padding: 48px 40px;
        }
        .author-card .avatar {
            width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4a747, #a08030);
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #0a0a0f; font-weight: 700;
        }
        .author-card h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .author-card .handle { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #d4a747; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .author-card p { color: #a09888; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }
        .author-card .quote {
            font-style: italic; color: #d4a747; margin-top: 24px;
            padding: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.15);
            border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* === RCP / CONTACT === */
        .rcp-section {
            text-align: center; padding: 60px 24px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.08);
        }
        .rcp-section .rcp-logo {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.4rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: #f0e8d8; margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .rcp-section .rcp-logo span { color: #d4a747; }
        .rcp-section p { color: #a09888; font-size: 0.9rem; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
        .rcp-section .contact-link { color: #d4a747; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.3); transition: border-color 0.3s; }
        .rcp-section .contact-link:hover { border-color: #d4a747; }

        /* === FOOTER === */
        footer { text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px; color: #605850; font-size: 0.8rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
        footer a { color: #a09888; }
        footer a:hover { color: #d4a747; }

        /* === MODAL === */
        .modal-overlay {
            display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 2000;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 24px;
        }
        .modal-overlay.active { display: flex; }
        .modal {
            background: #14141e; border: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.2);
            border-radius: 12px; max-width: 700px; width: 100%;
            max-height: 90vh; overflow-y: auto; padding: 40px; position: relative;
            animation: modalIn 0.3s ease;
        }
        .modal-close { position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 20px; background: none; border: none; color: #a09888; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; }
        .modal-close:hover { color: #f0e8d8; }
        .modal img { width: 100%; max-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .modal h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .modal .role { color: #d4a747; font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .modal p { color: #c0b8a8; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        @keyframes modalIn { from { transform: translateY(24px) scale(0.96); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; } }

        /* === RESPONSIVE === */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links { display: none; position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(10,10,15,0.98); flex-direction: column; padding: 24px; gap: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212,167,71,0.15); }
            .nav-links.active { display: flex; }
            .nav-toggle { display: block; }
            .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
            .story-image img { height: 280px; }
            .characters-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
            .character-card img { height: 200px; }
            .realms-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .modal { padding: 24px; }
            .author-card { padding: 32px 24px; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .characters-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .btn { display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ==================== NAVBAR ==================== -->
<nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
    <div class="nav-container">
        <div class="nav-logo">Sigillum <span>Maximum</span></div>
        <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
            <li><a href="#story">The Story</a></li>
            <li><a href="#characters">Characters</a></li>
            <li><a href="#realms">The Seven Realms</a></li>
            <li><a href="#author">The Author</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Menu">☰</button>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- ==================== HERO ==================== -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-tag">Roberto Calvo Productions Presents</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Sigillum <em>Maximum</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">The Seal of the Seven Secrets</p>
        <p class="hero-logline">
            "A princess. Seven seals. One choice that will save — or shatter — the Great Universal Realm."
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="#story" class="btn btn-primary">Discover the Story</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll" onclick="document.getElementById('story').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        Scroll <svg width="16" height="24" viewBox="0 0 16 24" fill="none" stroke="#a09888" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 8l6 8 6-8"/></svg>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ==================== LOGLINE BANNER ==================== -->
<section class="logline-banner">
    <p>
        <span class="highlight">Seven kingdoms.</span> Seven secrets.
        A <span class="highlight">black knight</span> who will stop at nothing.
        And a princess who <span class="highlight">must find the light</span>
        before the darkness consumes everything.
    </p>
</section>

<!-- ==================== THE STORY ==================== -->
<section class="section" id="story">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">The <span class="gold">Story</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">An epic journey across the Great Universal Realm</p>
        <div class="story-grid">
            <div class="story-image">
                <img src="images/1. AILEEN NELLA SUA CASETTA SULL'ALBERO.png" alt="Aileen in her treehouse" loading="lazy">
            </div>
            <div class="story-text">
                <h3>When the Darkness Came</h3>
                <p>
                    Princess Aileen is thirteen when a mysterious <strong>Black Knight</strong> invades her peaceful kingdom of Nuvolandia.
                    Her mother is turned to stone. Her father is taken captive. The ancient <strong>Sigillum Maximum</strong> —
                    the golden scroll upon which the security of all seven realms depends — has been stolen.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Sent through a hidden passage to the <strong>Elf Kingdom</strong>, Aileen must find the legendary
                    <strong>Aeltiàfisar</strong>, the Knight of the Golden Light. Together with the fierce orc <strong>Grogher</strong>
                    and the mysterious <strong>Dorcha</strong> — a boy with darkness in his blood — she embarks on a
                    perilous quest across the seven kingdoms of the Great Universal Realm.
                </p>
                <div class="quote">
                    "Seven trials. Seven secrets. Seven keys to saving a world."
                </div>
                <p>
                    From the cloud-cities of Nuvolandia to the underwater palaces of the Merpeople,
                    from the gnome kingdoms to the halls of the Elves — each realm holds a secret that
                    could break the curse. But time is running out. And the Black Knight is always watching.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ==================== CHARACTERS ==================== -->
<section class="section" id="characters" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01);">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">The <span class="gold">Characters</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Meet the heroes, villains, and magical companions</p>
        <div class="characters-grid" id="charactersGrid"></div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ==================== THE SEVEN REALMS ==================== -->
<section class="section" id="realms">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">The <span class="gold">Seven Realms</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">A universe built from light, shadow, and ancient magic</p>
        <div class="realms-grid">
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#e8d8b0;"><span class="rune">☁️</span><h4>Nuvolandia</h4><p>The Cloud Kingdom. A land of soft clouds, moonstone castles, and beings in constant telepathic contact with the skies. Home of Princess Aileen.</p></div>
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#7ec850;"><span class="rune">🌿</span><h4>Elf Kingdom</h4><p>An ancient realm of towering forests and luminous cities. Home to Aeltiàfisar, the Knight of the Golden Light, and King Baelkers.</p></div>
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#c0a060;"><span class="rune">⛰️</span><h4>Gnome Kingdom</h4><p>The Kingdom of the Two Rainbows. A subterranean realm of brilliant crystals, Pallafiocco tournaments, and ancient curses that still echo through the halls.</p></div>
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#4a80c0;"><span class="rune">🌊</span><h4>Merfolk Kingdom</h4><p>An underwater realm of coral palaces and mother-of-pearl gowns. The merpeople hold secrets of the deep that even the oldest elves do not know.</p></div>
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#806030;"><span class="rune">🏔️</span><h4>Dwarf Kingdom</h4><p>Forged in the heart of mountains. Masters of craft, stone, and ancient metallurgy. Their secret is one of the seven that Aileen must recover.</p></div>
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#404060;"><span class="rune">⚡</span><h4>Storm Kingdom</h4><p>A realm of perpetual tempests. Home to the orcs. A people of immense strength, deep loyalty, and a secret buried in thunder.</p></div>
            <div class="realm-card" style="--r-color:#f0e8d8;"><span class="rune">✨</span><h4>Realm of the Great Light</h4><p>The legendary domain where the Immortal Sovereigns retire. The source of the Sigillum Maximum's power. Few have seen it. None speak of it.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ==================== THE AUTHOR ==================== -->
<section class="section" id="author">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">The <span class="gold">Author</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">The voice behind the magic</p>
        <div class="author-section">
            <div class="author-card">
                <div class="avatar">EL</div>
                <h3>Eleanor Lian</h3>
                <p class="handle">Author &amp; Creator</p>
                <p>
                    Eleanor Lian is a storyteller who builds worlds where emotions have weight,
                    magic has rules, and every character carries a piece of the human heart.
                    <em>Sigillum Maximum — The Seal of the Seven Secrets</em> is her most ambitious
                    work: an epic fantasy that explores courage, loss, love, and the choices that
                    define who we become.
                </p>
                <div class="quote">
                    "There are stories that do not wait to be written — they happen.
                    They arrive like a silent call, like a force that passes through you
                    and asks only to be welcomed. Sigillum Maximum is one of them."
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ==================== RCP / CONTACT ==================== -->
<section class="rcp-section" id="contact">
